column2: SELECT ra,dec,u,g,r,i,z,extinction_u,extinction_g,extinction_r,extinction_i,extinction_z,Err_u,Err_g,Err_r,Err_i,Err_z,flag_i,flag_r,flag_g into complete_table_SDSS, distance(   POINT(&&&, MyTable.ra, MyTable.de),   POINT(&&&, DR1#.ra, DR1#.dec)) AS dist FROM SDSS.DR1# AS SDSS, MyTable AS Mytable WHERE #=CONTAINS(   POINT(&&&, MyTable.ra, MyTable.de),   CIRCLE(&&&, DR1#.ra, DR1#.dec, #) )
